(1424, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/05/wordpress-4-2-2/''>WordPress 4.2.2 Security and Maintenance Release</a> <span class="rss-date">May 7, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.2.2 is now available. This is a critical security release for all previous versions and we strongly encourage you to update your sites immediately. Version 4.2.2 addresses two security issues: The Genericons icon font package, which is used in a number of popular themes and plugins, contained an HTML file vulnerable to a cross-site [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/fast-page-switch-adds-a-quick-way-to-switch-between-pages-in-the-wordpress-backend''>WPTavern: Fast Page Switch Adds a Quick Way to Switch Between Pages in the WordPress Backend</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wpweekly-episode-194-celebrating-wordpress-12th-birthday-with-matt-mullenweg''>WPTavern: WPWeekly Episode 194 – Celebrating WordPress’ 12th Birthday with Matt Mullenweg</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/wordpress-theme-review-team-is-cracking-down-on-violations-of-the-presentation-vs-functionality-guideline''>WPTavern: WordPress Theme Review Team is Cracking Down on Violations of the Presentation vs. Functionality Guideline</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/photo-gallery/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>Photo Gallery</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=photo-gallery&amp;_wpnonce=dfbf4f18d8&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Photo Gallery''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
