stomer base in real-time that was also responsive and mobile-friendly. However, when PayNearMe came to Avenue Code, their resources were allocated to other projects, so they needed an external team to take charge of their web project. In this project, they needed a modern looking and fully responsive website. Creating a Wordpress site that was responsive, elegant, and functional on all devices across all operating systems was only possible with the assistance of a swift, and knowledgeable team.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2><b>The Journey </b></h2>\r\nAvenue Code joined PayNearMe and we were able to provide them with QA guidance. Our QA team provided the proper testing to ensure their site was everything they desired. We helped them find hidden bugs, and lay them to rest. PayNearMe needed everything done in lightening speed. With 30 percent of US consumers preferring cash as a tender, PayNearMe’s web presence is now able to bring cash payments into the 21st century with ease, by bridging the digital divide and allowing everyone to participate in the digital economy on PayNearMe’s responsive, mobile friendly website.', 'Case study: PayNearMe', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '169-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-12 18:26:23', '2015-05-12 18:26:23', '', 169, 'http://localhost/acnew/169-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
