 IT costs were decreased by $40 million</li>\r\n	<li>Project delivery increased by 300%</li>\r\n	<li>Company B saved 60% of IT costs</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Fortune 100 Retailer', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '187-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-12 19:47:09', '2015-05-12 19:47:09', '', 187, 'http://localhost/acnew/187-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
