(285, 1, '2015-05-21 20:24:02', '2015-05-21 20:24:02', '<p class="releaseDateline" style="color: #000000;">San Francisco, CA (PRWEB) January 09, 2014</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Avenue Code, an IT consulting firm specializing in <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdmVudWVjb2RlLmNvbQ==" rel="nofollow">agile software development methodologies</a>, announces that it recently opened its third office in Brazil—this time in São Paulo—in addition to two existing locations in Belo Horizonte.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Avenue Code sees the expansion in Brazil as a timely strategic movement in light of the nation’s booming economy. With a planned expenditure of US $35 billion for three new soccer stadiums, Brazil expects to reap huge economical benefits from the 2014 World Cup. In addition, Brazil is to host the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, bringing the nation to the attention of investors and businesses worldwide.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">With its new offices located in Jardins, the prestigious business district in São Paulo, Avenue Code plans to cater to the tech-hungry organizations in the area. São Paulo, aka the “Concrete Jungle,” established its fame as the technology hub of South America, largely due to the presence of numerous international technology companies such as Airbnb, Google, and Walmart Brazil.</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">Marking the company’s largest expansion, the São Paulo office strategically positions Avenue Code in the upcoming year for engagements with Latin American clients and North American clients based in Brazil. Avenue Code’s co-founder Zeo Solomon explains, “To date we have catered predominantly to clients in North America from our Brazilian development center in Belo Horizonte; but the São Paulo location will unlock new opportunities for Latin American clients, a region of increasing importance to the global economy.”</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">The newest executive to join Avenue Code, Alexandre Bioza, Head of Business and Consulting in Brazil, adds: “Since we opened in Brazil four years ago, our business has rapidly grown and we are now focused on expanding our client base in São Paulo, the largest business center of South America. We provide IT services for both near and on-shore clients and we are set to grow and aggressively compete with our innovative and agile business model.”</p>\r\n<p style="color: #000000;">About Avenue Code:\r\nAvenue Code is a <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Avenue Code" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL3d3dy5hdmVudWVjb2RlLmNvbQ==" rel="nofollow">full-service information technology consulting</a> and development organization that specializes in Agile Methodologies. We have been serving dozens of fortune 100 eCommerce companies, with a breadth of experience in <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Service Offerings" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL2F2ZW51ZWNvZGUuY29tL3NlcnZpY2VzLmh0bWw=" rel="nofollow">eCommerce</a>, <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Omni-channel technology" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL2F2ZW51ZWNvZGUuY29tL2NvbnRlbnQvb21uaS1jaGFubmVs" rel="nofollow">omni-channel technology</a>, and <a style="color: #07689b;" title="Mobile Development" href="http://www.prweb.net/Redirect.aspx?id=aHR0cDovL2F2ZW51ZWNvZGUuY29tL01vYmlsZV9EZXZlbG9wbWVudA==" rel="nofollow">mobile development</a>. Our solutions help our clients build sustainable success.</p>', 'San Francisco–based IT Consulting Company, Avenue Code, Makes a Strategic Expansion in Brazil by Opening Its Third Office', 'Avenue Code makes a strategic decision to expand its Brazil presence to São Paulo, its third office in Brazil following the earlier establishment of two offices in Belo Horizonte.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'san-francisco-based-it-consulting-company-avenue-code-makes-a-strategic-expansion-in-brazil-by-opening-its-third-office', '', '', '2015-05-21 20:24:02', '2015-05-21 20:24:02', '', 0, 'http://localhost/acnew/?post_type=release&#038;p=285', 0, 'release', '', 0);
